text: Zdzisław Lesiński (19 September 1921 - 22 August 2000) was a Polish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Poznań
